TextEng: I need to see the Source Stone.
I would like to ask you some questions.
Me need see stone.
Me want ask questions.
Goodbye.
What do you know about the Source Stone?
What you know 'bout Source Stone?
Where are the Words of Power?
Where be Power Words?
Who are you again?
Who you be again?
Don't you think it might be dangerous to unlock the secrets of the Source Stone?
Text: 근원석의 비밀을 푸는 게 위험할 수도 있다고 생각하지 않아?

TextEng: You not think it dangerous to unlock secrets of stone?
Text: 너 돌 비밀 푸는 게 위험하다고 생각 안 해?

TextEng: How come nobody noticed this stone down here before?
Text: 왜 전엔 아무도 이 돌을 눈치채지 못했지?

TextEng: This stone be here long time. How come no one see it 'til now?
Text: 돌 여기 오래 있었어. 왜 지금까지 아무도 안 봤어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> You feel the call of the ancient evil that dwells within the stone, Master Ford. Beware lest it consume you.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 포드 박사, 당신은 돌 안에 깃든 고대의 악이 부르는 소리를 느낍니다. 그것에 잠식되지 않도록 조심하세요.

TextEng: Tell me your theories.
Me want hear your theories.
I'm not interested in your theories.
Me not interested in you theory.
